result.formatted_address: 42 Sun Chun St, Tai Hang, Hong Kong
result.name: Taylor Shellfish Farms

reviews.text: A shellfish restaurant, can have different kinds of oysters and other kinds of seafood here, the seafood was fresh and taste good. There are only a few tables with limited seats here. The restaurant was an open area and it would be a bit hot during summer time.
good food, reasonable price
Great place with fresh seafood and very casual polite staff. Great!!

Popular for oysters, so we tried 3 types from small to large- French, French & Australia. All are delicious. And the seafood platter is fantastic, very freshly and tasty. The America mussels cooked with white wine also delicious as well. Final the birthday dessert is special offer from the restaurant that we didn’t expected, we just said it’s a birthday dinner when booking the table from OpenRice app. The whole dinner was great experience, services also good too.
Casual dining place with huge choices of seafood 🦞 🍤🦞🦐🦑🐙🐟🐠🐡
